-Hey.
-Isn't it tasty?

22
00:02:20,890 --> 00:02:22,350
Lie down and rest.

23
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:24,940
-Give me more booze!
-Yes.

24
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:26,360
Here you go.

25
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,320
Son-in-law?

26
00:02:28,650 --> 00:02:30,490
-Have another.
-Pour me some more!

27
00:02:30,570 --> 00:02:33,490
Look at this guy.

28
