MS. LEE SINA

39
00:04:46,370 --> 00:04:47,620
MS. LEE SINA

40
00:04:47,710 --> 00:04:48,620
Why should I?

41
00:04:48,710 --> 00:04:50,210
Why should I apologize?

42
