58
00:06:10,210 --> 00:06:11,460
For yourself,

59
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,420
look up at the sky,

60
00:06:15,420 --> 00:06:16,800
look at the flowers,

61
00:06:18,340 --> 00:06:19,800
