62
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:22,430
and dance too.

63
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,810
Just for yourself.

64
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:35,400
That's how you should die, Sina.

65
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:34,040
What am I doing here?

66
00:07:35,370 --> 00:07:37,040
What was I thinking?

67
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:38,790
Why did I come here?

68
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,760
You brat, it's so late!

69
00:07:49,850 --> 00:07:51,850
I don't want to go home today.

70
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:54,020
Hey, why are you so wasted?

71
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:55,730
I'm going to marry you.

72
00:07:55,810 --> 00:07:56,850
-What?
-Sir.

73
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:58,650
-It's not like that.
-You punk!

74
00:07:58,730 --> 00:08:00,900
You darn punk!

75
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:03,320
-Please.
-Out of my way, I'm going to kill you!

76
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:05,530
That's nonsense, you punk.

77
00:08:05,610 --> 00:08:07,320
Okay, understood.

78
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,240
You punk.

79
00:08:24,260 --> 00:08:25,630
He's human after all.

80
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:29,180
Even Mr. Noh Manners

81
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:31,600
is a human like me.

82
00:08:33,010 --> 00:08:35,640
He licks the lid
of the yogurt cup like me,

83
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:41,020
