with a stretched-out collar like me,

84
00:08:44,820 --> 00:08:47,900
and laughs… like me too.

85
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:13,300
Yes.

86
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:17,060
It wasn't your fault…

87
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,810
